author: Sam Sutton
title: Protesters assemble in front of New Jersey Statehouse to assail stay-at-home order
description: The words "No more fear" were audible through a megaphone as a helicopter hovered overhead and law enforcement officers blocked access to the Statehouse parking complex.
content:
Tweet capturing the protest from the New Jersey Chamber of Commerce.
Demonstrators gathered in downtown Trenton, N.J., Friday morning to protest Gov. Phil Murphy's "stay-at-home" order to combat the spread of coronavirus.
